---
title: Garlic Pan-Seared Halloumi Sandwich with Baby Heirloom Tomato Salad
description: We've added a fresh and tasty baby heirloom tomato salad to this refreshing halloumi sandwich! This dish features a simple yet satisfying herby mayo and decadent zucchini ribbons.
